Tech Stack: Python | Streamlit | EasyOCR | SQLite/MySQL

Overview:
BizCardX is a Streamlit web app that extracts and manages data from business card images using Optical Character Recognition (OCR). It simplifies the digitization of business cards, enabling users to easily upload images, extract contact details, and store them in a database.

Key Features:

Upload business card images via a user-friendly Streamlit GUI

Extract key details using EasyOCR: Name, Company, Designation, Phone, Email, Website, Address

Display extracted data in an organized layout

Store data and card image in a database (SQLite/MySQL)

Perform CRUD operations (Create, Read, Update, Delete) directly from the app

Simple and intuitive interface for seamless interaction

Cleanly structured, scalable, and maintainable codebase

This project demonstrates skills in OCR, image processing, database integration, and interactive web app development.
